@startuml
title IterLife Reunion 文章发布流程主链路图
autonumber "<b>[000]"

skinparam Shadowing false
skinparam sequence {
  ParticipantPadding 16
  BoxPadding 10
  ArrowThickness 1
  LifeLineBorderColor #6B7280
  LifeLineBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  ParticipantBorderColor #475569
  ParticipantBackgroundColor #FFFFFF
  GroupBorderColor #94A3B8
  GroupBackgroundColor #F8FAFC
}

legend right
|= 执行归属 |= 说明 |
| 用户本地 | 作者在本地编辑 Markdown 并 push |
| GitHub 侧 | 远端仓库、Webhook 投递、Contents/Compare API |
| IterLife Reunion 系统 | 验签、异步编排、解析、投影、索引同步 |
endlegend

box "用户本地" #E8F5E9
  actor "作者" as Author
end box

box "GitHub 侧" #FFF8E1
  participant "GitHub 仓库" as GitHubRepo
  participant "GitHub Webhook" as GitHubWebhook
  participant "GitHub API" as GitHubApi
end box

box "IterLife Reunion 系统" #E3F2FD
  participant "WebhookController\nWebhook 接收器" as WebhookController
  participant "GithubSignatureService\n签名校验服务" as SignatureService
  participant "ArticlePublishEventService\n发布事件服务" as PublishEventService
  participant "ArticlePublishEventRepository\n发布事件仓储" as PublishEventRepo
  participant "publishEventTaskExecutor\n发布线程池" as PublishExecutor
  participant "ArticleSyncService\n文章同步服务" as SyncService
  participant "ArticleFrontmatterService\nFrontMatter 处理服务" as FrontmatterService
  participant "FrontMatterParserService\nFrontMatter 解析服务" as ParserService
  participant "ArticleRepository\n文章仓储" as ArticleRepository
  participant "MeilisearchIndexService\n搜索索引服务" as MeiliService
end box

== 发布入口 ==

Author -> GitHubRepo: 推送 Markdown 变更
GitHubRepo -> GitHubWebhook: 生成 push 事件
GitHubWebhook -> WebhookController: 调用 POST /api/webhook/github/push
WebhookController -> SignatureService: 校验 HMAC 签名

alt 签名通过？否
  SignatureService --> WebhookController: 非法
  WebhookController --> GitHubWebhook: 401
else 签名通过
  SignatureService --> WebhookController: 合法
  WebhookController -> WebhookController: 解析 rawBody 为 GithubPushEvent
  alt 载荷解析成功？否
    WebhookController --> GitHubWebhook: 400
  else 载荷解析成功
    WebhookController -> PublishEventService: 接收入库请求
    PublishEventService -> PublishEventRepo: 写入 article_publish_event(RECEIVED)
    PublishEventService -> PublishEventRepo: 标记 DISPATCHING
    PublishEventService -> PublishExecutor ++: 提交 eventId
    WebhookController --> GitHubWebhook: 202 Accepted(eventId)
  end
end

PublishExecutor -> SyncService ++: processPersistedEvent(eventId)

== 文件变更发现 ==

SyncService -> SyncService: 校验仓库与分支是否允许同步
alt 应继续同步？否
  SyncService -> SyncService: 结束处理
else 应继续同步
  SyncService -> FrontmatterService: 识别是否为 normalizer replay 事件
  FrontmatterService --> SyncService: replay 判定结果

  SyncService -> SyncService: 从 commits[] 收集 Markdown 路径
  alt commit 文件列表存在？否
    SyncService -> GitHubApi: 调用 compare API 获取变更文件
    GitHubApi --> SyncService: 返回 changed 路径与 removed 路径
  else commit 文件列表存在
    SyncService -> SyncService: 使用 commit 自带文件列表
  end

  SyncService -> SyncService: 执行 removedPaths -= changedPaths

  loop for each removed path
    SyncService -> ArticleRepository: 按 repo + path 逻辑删除文章
    alt 找到活跃文章？是
      ArticleRepository --> SyncService: 返回 articleId
      SyncService -> MeiliService: 删除对应搜索索引文档
    else 找到活跃文章？否
      ArticleRepository --> SyncService: 跳过删除
    end
  end

== 文章拉取与投影 ==

  loop for each changed path
    SyncService -> GitHubApi: 调用 contents API 拉取正文
    alt 正文拉取成功？否
      GitHubApi --> SyncService: 404 / 非 2xx
      SyncService -> SyncService: 记录日志并跳过该路径
    else 正文拉取成功
      GitHubApi --> SyncService: 返回 markdown 与 blob sha

      alt replay 事件？否
        SyncService -> FrontmatterService: 执行 FrontMatter 规范化判定
        FrontmatterService --> SyncService: 返回待投影文件列表
      else replay 事件
        SyncService -> SyncService: 直接使用当前变更文件
      end

      SyncService -> ParserService: 解析 FrontMatter 与正文元数据
      alt 解析成功？否
        ParserService --> SyncService: 空结果
        SyncService -> SyncService: parseSkipped++
      else 解析成功
        ParserService --> SyncService: ArticleMeta
        SyncService -> ArticleRepository: 查询当前活跃快照与标签
        ArticleRepository --> SyncService: 返回快照与标签
        SyncService -> SyncService: 执行重复投影判定
        alt 属于重复投影？是
          SyncService -> SyncService: unchangedSkip++
        else 属于重复投影？否
          SyncService -> ArticleRepository: upsert 文章与标签映射
          ArticleRepository --> SyncService: article 与 article_tag 已更新
          SyncService -> MeiliService: upsert 搜索索引
        end
      end
    end
  end
end

== 主链路结束 ==

SyncService -> SyncService: 记录 changed/removed/projected 统计

@enduml
